{"tid":2319963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"初步確診女警曾到九龍城學校區派傳單","createTime":"2020-12-10T12:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T13:19:38.000Z","uid":230530,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0a84dd1c2b323e62c958197a3da485f9ef3d57","tid":2319963,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"警方昨日公布，一名駐守新界南防止罪案辦公室的43歲女警，初步確診新型冠狀病毒。警方表示，經進一步了解，得悉女警曾於上月26日在九龍城區一間學校派發傳單，期間全程配戴口罩。警方了解事件後已立即通知相關學校，並會繼續與衞生署和學校保持緊密聯繫。 警方指，女警星期一不適，到政府診所求醫，昨日得知初步確診，女警星期二最後一日上班，過去14日沒有外遊。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2370155&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=01edca3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370155</a>"},{"pid":"06f913ad0e98726bc5e1281d6535fddb23c9abd8","tid":2319963,"uid":143241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"累人累物,唔死都無用"},{"pid":"3d41eca6c0192709e22c5efb3d3ec50826498d81","tid":2319963,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06f913ad0e98726bc5e1281d6535fddb23c9abd8","tid":2319963,"uid":143241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"累人累物,唔死都無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad190ca911f891f4731ea5d74ee94db7b4484fb","tid":2319963,"uid":198181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d0a84dd1c2b323e62c958197a3da485f9ef3d57","tid":2319963,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"警方昨日公布，一名駐守新界南防止罪案辦公室的43歲女警，初步確診新型冠狀病毒。警方表示，經進一步了解，得悉女警曾於上月26日在九龍城區一間學校派發傳單，期間全程配戴口罩。